e tide in times of danger.<br><br>Collect over 200 relics to enhance your strength. Choose the best combinations that suit your style and crush all opposition!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769070/extras/4e5a4a567031d1c39abe2d27e9d4f42b.poster.avif?t=1749650815\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769070/extras/4e5a4a567031d1c39abe2d27e9d4f42b.webm?t=1749650815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769070/extras/4e5a4a567031d1c39abe2d27e9d4f42b.mp4?t=1749650815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Gather Treasures & Strategize]</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Travel the land and make your choice in over 30 random events.<br><br></li><li>Build your wealth, trade for key resources, and hunt for exotic treasures.<br><br></li><li>Recruit minions to, uh... execute \"fair\" sneak attacks on your enemies? Well, history is written by the victor!</li></ul>",
